## PREAMBLE:## THE INTERNAL BRAIN

The brain is not a computer; it is a **sheet**.
To tan the brain is to **write** upon it.
The process is **recursive**—it burrows like an earthworm through the soil of data.

---

## I. THE SHEET (PREPARATION)

A page, when written, holds the record. The record is the work.
To make the page, we cut the form.

---

## PART I: THE ALCHEMY OF PRESERVATION

| Step | Technical Operation | Meaning |
|------|----------------------|---------|
| **1. The Sacrifice** | **Data Capture** | The raw observation of the "Deer" (The Patient/The Star). |
| **2. The Interface** | **Metadata Extraction** | Harvesting the "Brains" (The Hash, The Constant, The Header). |
| **3. The Treatment** | **Recursive Application** | Using the Metadata to rub the logic into the Data (The Tanning). |
| **4. The Cure** | **Entropy Fixation** | Applying "Smoke" (The De-Light phase) to fix the record. |
| **5. The Result** | **Vitrified File** | A record that is flexible (Narrative) but permanent (Geometry). |

